==== OpenRC ====

To enable the service to run at system boot:

{{RootCmd|rc-update add rsyncd default}}

To start the rsync daemon now:

{{RootCmd|rc-service rsyncd start}}

==== systemd ====

To enable the service to run at system boot:

{{RootCmd|systemctl enable rsyncd.service}}

To start the rsync daemon now:

{{RootCmd|systemctl start rsyncd.service}}

